# Portfolio conventions

- Content editable data → `content/`. Sections in `app/components/sections/` are presentational only.
- UI primitives → `app/components/ui/`.
- No new npm dependencies without explicit approval.
- Static site only — no API routes, no server actions with side effects.
- External links: `target="_blank"` + `rel="noopener noreferrer"`.
- Images: use `next/image` through `Avatar` or add optimized `Image` usage.
- Tailwind utility classes; avoid custom CSS unless necessary.
- English content, outcome-oriented tone.
- Run `yarn build` after substantive changes.
